Title: SoundFontLoad
JsName: addSoundFontLoad();removeSoundFontLoad()
DomName: alphaTab.soundFontLoad
Category: Events - Player
Description: This event is fired when the SoundFont is being loaded.
ShowInSideBar: false
Since: 0.9.4
